@startuml US_2.2.4_SSD
autonumber

actor "Port Authority\nOfficer" as Officer
participant ":System" as System

== Register Storage Area ==
activate Officer
Officer -> System: Clica na secção "Storage Areas"
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta página com lista de storage areas e opção "Register Storage Area"
deactivate System
Officer -> System: Clica em "Register Storage Area"
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta formulário de registo de storage area
deactivate System
Officer -> System: Introduz dados da storage area (name, areaType, location, maxCapacity, servedDocks, distances) e submete
activate System
System --> Officer: devolve mensagem de sucesso ou erro
deactivate System

== Update Storage Area ==
Officer -> System: Seleciona storage area da lista
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta detalhes da storage area
deactivate System
Officer -> System: Clica em "Edit Storage Area"
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta formulário de edição preenchido
deactivate System
Officer -> System: Modifica dados da storage area e submete
activate System
System --> Officer: devolve mensagem de sucesso ou erro
deactivate System

== Search Storage Areas ==
Officer -> System: Introduz critérios de pesquisa (name, type, location)
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta lista de storage areas filtradas
deactivate System
deactivate Officer

@enduml
